description:
WE ARE THE BRIDGE!

The Bridge is the largest network of digital professionals in LATAM with more than 230 thousand rockstars. Startups, scale-ups, large companies and consultancies from all over the world work with us to achieve the most challenging and impactful projects. Are you ready to participate in the challenge?

🔧 The Position.

We are looking for the next game changer to join the team as SR. Full Stack Developer. To consider this role you must be located in Brazil.

We are looking for a highly skilled, mission-driven individual with unlimited drive and enthusiasm for digital transformation

Requirements

✨ You will be responsible:

• Design, develop and modify systems taking into account the service architecture;
• Analyze user needs to determine how software should be built or if existing software should be modified;
• Transform requirements and specifications into software;
• Participate in design and code reviews;
• Contribute to the development of both backend and... front-end systems;
• Implement cloud systems following the Serverless philosophy whenever possible;
• Document planned and implemented resources in order to optimize communication between team members;
• Implement automatic mechanisms to ensure that what has been implemented complies with what has been specified.

✅ It is important that you have knowledge and/or experience in:

• Knowledge of algorithms and data structures;
• Experience in full stack development using React, Node.js, Typescript and Python;
• Proven development experience using AWS, Azure or GCloud providers;
• Implementation experience using Docker and/or FaaS;
• Familiarity with different types of databases including SQL, NoSQL, ElasticSearch, and Cache;
• Knowledge of version control using Git;
• Knowledge of CI/CD;
• Experience writing unit and integration tests;
• Excellent writing and communication skills;
• Ability to collaborate with high-functioning teams and individuals to achieve common goals.

🚀 It's a plus if you know/experience in:

• Well-Architected Framework;
• Candidates with one or more AWS certificates.

📌 This process will be conducted considering the following steps:

• Application Evaluation;
• Chat with the People and Culture team;
• Chat with the Team Manager.
• The steps mentioned above may change according to the progress of the selection process. But don't worry, we will always be updating you :)

Do you think this challenge is for you? Click on "Apply for Vacancy", we are waiting for you! 🤩🚀💙

